### Phase 3: Auth & Legal Pages

#### [NEW] `src/app/(auth)/login/page.tsx` & `src/app/(auth)/register/page.tsx`
*   *(Note: Assuming we place auth under an `(auth)` group for layout isolation, or integrate them into `(public)` if they share the exact same layout. We will likely use a dedicated centered-card layout without the marketing footer).*
*   **Design:** Simple, centered card with email/password inputs and OAuth buttons. Professional, clean borders.

#### [NEW] `src/app/(auth)/forgot-password/page.tsx` & `src/app/(auth)/reset-password/page.tsx`
*   **Design:** Standard functional forms matching the login card aesthetic.

#### [NEW] `src/app/(public)/privacy-policy/page.tsx`, `src/app/(public)/terms-of-service/page.tsx`, `src/app/(public)/contact/page.tsx`
*   **Design:** `prose` (Tailwind Typography) styled long-form text content. Narrow maximum width (`max-w-3xl`) for optimal reading. The Contact page will feature a structured form and support email listing.

