## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
*   Run `npm run lint` and `npm run build` to ensure no Type errors or missing imports are introduced across the new pages.

### Manual Verification
*   Review all new routes (`/`, `/templates`, `/pricing`, `/features`, `/login`, etc.) in the local dev environment.
*   Verify responsive behavior (mobile, tablet, desktop) on the Home page and Pricing grid.
*   Audit the final output against the "Professional SaaS" constraints:
    *   No overly large fonts.
    *   No excessive whitespace.
    *   No generic marketing buzzwords.
    *   Appropriate structural hierarchy and contrast.
